Sure, here are some example sentences in Serbian that use the word "sredini" in different forms and positions:

1. *Sredini* godine, odlučio sam da promenim svoj život. (In the middle of the year, I decided to change my life.)
2. Nalazim se u *sredini* knjige koju čitam. (I am in the middle of the book I am reading.)
3. *Sredinom* marta putovaću u Beograd. (In the middle of March, I will travel to Belgrade.)
4. Ova soba ima prozor na *sredini* zida. (This room has a window in the middle of the wall.)
5. *Sredinom* predavanja, profesor je pozvao studente da postave pitanja. (In the middle of the lecture, the professor invited students to ask questions.)
6. U *sredini* trga nalazi se fontana. (In the middle of the square there is a fountain.)
7. *Sredinom* nedelje idem na aerodrom da dočekam prijatelja. (Midweek I am going to the airport to pick up a friend.)

